values:
1[ you'd be suprised at how much i actually think of you first. believe what ever you want but i know that im doing the right thing. dont be suprised when i act like i could careless. cause 1) honestly, i dont and 2) i dont want to have to deal with all the drama you bring along with everything. dont agree with me, i know you wont. you're good at that. don't expect anything from me until your mature enough to talk about things rather than argue. ]

2[ tonight was wow. good. overwelming. my heart was like beating out of my chest. good night. crazy. i wont be sharing details=). HA HA. to bad for you buddy ;).]

went to the ga-ga-ga-game tonite! first coast BabY. it was fun. finally saw my love LISA. shes so great. and her bf is so nice. and hott. and old. and has a car. lol i am jealous if u can tell. ;-)  =). it was a lot of fun though. saw the new love of my life and my best best friend and my best friend. haha n every1 else. the new love of my life is wonderuful. i miss the BCrush though (sandi!). he's so wonderful. seriously. i adore this boy. i miss him. haha it hasn't even been like an hour since i talked to him. Kelly is ppaaathetticc. oh well=). things are so different this year. im starting to adapt to it. feels like nothing is less than it was. im greatful though. =). i can't sleep tonite. i love you. <3kelly

KELLY IS A LIVE JOURNAL LOSER! 2 times in one night. pathetic, oh well. =). so i am feeling better. talked to brandi, lexi, n tracey. love them<3. good news! pictures finally came on slantways! bad news.. U-G-L-Y. the 1st one is just awful n the 2nd one is alrite. the site is : http://slantways.com/Jacksonville/5 Points/hypnotique/Gallery_1/index.htm

im girl # 17. haha. dont like the outfit either. camo=never cute. i shoulda put eye liner under my eyes n then i coulda been a warrior. haha that would have been pretty. just my opinion.

i dont think im going to take any of what you say to heart any more. was your goal to try and get me to like you or something. do you find it amusing to make me like you and then act like im a stranger the next day. i dont think its amusing at all. actually, i think that its horrible. to bad for you i only semi care, and to bad for you that i didnt even want what you claimed you wanted. i never said i did and i think thats what bothered you. i think im done pretending like everything is like it was, because its truly not and im starting to think that it never will be. actually i never thought it would be. tell me im being negative, i know you want to. i dare you. tell me that n see what i say. stop acting like nothing happened or dont talk to me at all.

=) im A ok now. hah i think i sound so like..mean on this thing. n im not. i just dont want to push my problems onto ne1 else so i write it in these dumb online diarys wen i get bored. great concept! everyone is happy.

shiny happy people dancing..lalala shiny happy people holding hands. <-- the most wonderful song in the world! makes me think of like thanksgiving.. haha. ne way.

this is a really long entry. so ive decided what i want to do with my life. hah well not really but im really into politics. [this is where my entry gets boring, just warning you=)] i watched the debate between bush n kerry n i was like wow! i wish i could debate like that. kerry did marvolous though i couldnt hear him half the time b/c my mother wouldnt stop like effing worshipping him. hardcore democrat. dont know how many times i told her to be quiet! =)

so school is really gay this year. every day is almost exactly the same. i really like the song by "the used" --> the taste of ink. the beginning is really good. like the lyrics too.

so much has changed this year. in the past 2 months. its so crazy thinking about it. i dont like thinking about it.

its just not fair sometimes. some1 else is living my dream and all i can do is watch from the sidelines as everything ive ever wanted is being shattered to.. nothing.

im such a drama queen somtimes. haha geeeezzzzuusss. i really dont like being a girl. boys are like chill n im over here obsessing over stupid stuff. oh well. i am b-o-r-e-d. im suprised if you've read this far.

i really want to get back on track with everything. school, friends, family, my room is looking awful these days, and just even the little things. im not living up my expectations at all and i dont really know where to start.

im looking at ur picture. makes me want to cry. and throw up. great combination. its upsetting how a simple picture, a simple glance at it can make me feel like this. makes me feel light headed almost. your gonna kill me. "you kill me, you know you do you kill me well. you like it too and i can tell". EXACTLY. haha.. man, i really cant sleep.

i really miss you at paxon. i think about you all the time. makes me sad that your gone.. ill never forget all of our memories. i love you dearly.

i think that this is possibly the longest entry ive ever written. im making a record. how exciting.

im telling the guy at slantways that i want retakes. i got the right moves now and no mo wearin camo. haha. good plan, yeah? yeah. show him some of my flava. haha barbie.com is quite fun. you can go to the "flavas" section and get a new name. my name is K-BOO. fits me wonderfully. i would like you to call me that, along with: girl #17, KC (kacee), Kel, Arial, Jo-Jo, Red and the numerous other names ppl call me. keep it nice though. "bitch" is not acceptable.

i think i made you mad. hah and you dont think you deserve it? funny, cause i do. i actually think its hilarious. yeah, im dieing of laughter over here. nice of you to wait for me and then leave w/o saying any thing. yeah, that was real friendly. since we're "good friends" again and all right? waiting to see how long i would take to come back? dumb. im satisfied.

wow i need to go to bed. pmsing is killing me and i ahvnt slept in a week. sorry im so grumpy. hate me. it will be fun. good night. <3kelly

im having such an off night. no reason really, just kind of bummed i guess. not really because of you, but because of me. its my fault things are the way they are. i act like i have no control over what goes on in my life and i do. it was up to me and i blew it. even if it was the smallest chance in the world.. i still had it and i didnt use it to my advantage. instead i made silly excuses as to why i shouldnt go for it. i lost what i had been waiting for, for so long and now its beyond to late. im so dissappointed in myself and sad about the fact that i could be doing something so much more entertaining than sitting here sulking about things that arent going to change. i beginning to think that there was nothing there in the first place.

i cant look at your picture. your the 8th picture down and all i keep doing is glancing at the stack n then feeling like im being crushed all over again. this is quite fun. i love spending my saterday nights thinking about you and all the things that could have happened but never will. this is beyond pathetic and i hate with a passion online diarys.

they pass the time though. i just want to fast forward to the part where we fall in love and live happily ever after. i think that is just to much to ask for though. my imagination is running away with me tonite. blah.

i wish i knew how you felt about me. what you really thought. whether its good or bad i just want to know. sometimes i can't tell if you really hate me or if you just act like it but really you dont think im that bad. i dont get you at all and im afraid to ask. im afraid to like talk to you. i dont want to make things worse. i have this dumb idea of how we would be n it simply wont go away. why do i like some1 that im afraid to talk to? no idea. i wont deny it ne more though. no matter how much i dont want to feel this way, i do. im fucking pathetic.

im listening to brand new and i love them. i just feel like crying. maybe that will make me feel better. i dont deserve you. i dont deserve you at all :'(. <3kelly

this song makes me so sad:'(. i wish you werent horrible, horrible to me. i fell for all the empty words you said.

well i just got home. went home early.. school is just not poppin these days. its sad to once had loved something with everything you had to only grow to hate it. oh well. life goes on.

67 n math. im dissappointed. the more i try the worse i do. i think ive just decided that im simply dumb. half kidding. blah, no big=)

so i think ill write an entry that actually means something rather then the norm "today was a good day! yippee skippy". but today in fact was good..me,tracey,sandis talk this morning-priceless=). but moving on..

ill start off with you(girl). you know.. i think that its terrible how you put on an act like that. maybe i was naive to think that you actually wanted to be friends with me b/c of me? thats what normal people do. i think its horrible how you put yourself out to be some one your not by far. your no better than anyone else and i find it funny that you think you are. your intentions were way unneccesary and i dont know why i was there for you in the first place. i thought you were a great person but you have totally proven me wrong and i have zerroo respect for you.

next!=). you (guy). well.. i know i already told you this but im sorry. i honestly don't know why i was being bitter and i didnt mean for it to go on for as long as it did. i just want us to go back to how we were. i hope you stick to your word.. waiting for your call. =/ =). <3

#3 (guy). heh well.. dont really know where to start on this one. its hard trying to determine whether its you that i like.. or the idea of you that i like. maybe a little of both? i dont know any more, dont think i ever did really. you are by far the most confusing person ive ever met. or i could just be me making you out to be that. either way you confuse me greatly. heh its not ur fault though, you dont even do anything. i dont get it. im okay without you but i feel better with you. i hope im making sense.

haha i just wrote 68 reasons why i like you (i went into detail ha). i make lists when i am bored. what a waste of time but it amuses me for a while. im looking forward to tomorrow and the weekend. =). everything is good. <3kelly

so i was reading my last 3 entrys and wow.. i dont think i could get ne grumpier! well i just want to say that i am so glad that i had the chance to see the good side of you. you can be a great person when you want to be and i promise i wont think of you as anything differently. i listened to you.. i want you to know that.. im holding on to every word you said. though we were never ne thing you have made one of the hugest impacts on me. ill wait for you to feel the same things that i feel for you. so felt like i needed to say that. my weekend has been really good. today brandi was supossed to come over but jeanne is ruining that!=(. tear, miss her dearly. i was gonna go see shannon this morning but i needed to shower n stuff n she had work so blah. i miss her a lot. its weird saying "aw i talked to shannon tonite!" like its not a normal everyday thing. i let everything important to me slip away. grand isnt it? =) so i am 'reflecting' on everything. i dont know how i did it but all the time i was wasteing on you totally made me absent minded as to what was happening to me outside of how i felt about you. dont you just hate when that happens. i sure do. makes me sad actually. i wont show it. i wouldnt flatter yourself. i think i hate online diarys. i think i hate hurricanes too when i dont have ne thing better to do than to sit and write about pointless things. i think i need to find something to do to keep me busy. you will def. never read this. you mean so much to me. <3kelly

so my "good day" has totally been bombed and shot down about 43958 times now. brittney was supossed to come over but she had surgery..=/.. i really hope shes ok.. kinda scary. didnt expect to hear that wen i called. =/. well ne way so then i was supossed to go to the concert with lexi. parentals werent having it. i am really bummed out right about now. everytime i start thinking that your not what i thought you were i just get proved wrong again. i feel dissappointed all over again, n even more heart broken then i was. im not as upset as i was though.. no big deal right. im in the process of forgetting a.k.a acting like it never happened. and since i just love doing this so much maybe ill just 'forget' that i ever learned ur name, much less talked to you. yeah, i think that sounds like a great plan. what do you think? oh thats right, you dont care WHAT SO EVER. my bad i must have forgotten between my crying (its harder to think) and trying to remember what not and what im supossed to forget. since you decide that for me in all. if its not about you then i dont know who its about b/c it sure doesnt seem like its about me. im so mad.. not at you. im not mad at you at all, im just mad that i let myself fall this hard. that i let myself care this much. you didnt do ne thing wrong. your entitled to your oppinion and i completley understand what u were saying. i just didnt like it=(. at all.. but its no big. heh its not like your all that i think about right. its not like for the past month every thing that ive written in here is about you. im crying for no reason. really, i am(sarcasm). your just some random person that isnt to fond of me. and that is why ive written a page about you. any minute now would be the time for me to stop caring. you'll never read this. :'( <3kelly --theres no such thing as 2nd chances, your so beautiful..did u hear a word i said, i guess this is what i get--

everytime i read it all i can do is just shake my head. i am so speechless. you never stop amazing me and that is definitley not a compliment. you comfirmed everything i already thought so i dont know why i am so unbelievably shocked. i cant sleep. i talked to shannon tonite=). that was nice.. shes happy.. im happy for her. that is how our conversation went. i am in a horrible mood. have been ever since i had to go off with the family. only plus was i went to burger king and i got a yu gi oh toy. i was excited. me and my sister battled. kidding. i really cant sleep. great day at school. i should have never came home. i wish my power would have stayed out.. shoulda took the hint but then again im pretty dumb latley n dont know wen its the right time to just let it go. i know now. im not going to repeat myself ne more. you'll never see this. <3kelly

**MOST PATHETIC ENTRY I HAVE EVER WRITTEN! heh and that is why 2/3 of it is deleted. just left the main points of it i guess u could say. =)** so much for my heart being in one piece. i want to hate you like you hate me. i think your worth waiting for. i know your worth waiting for.. --theres no such thing as second chances*your so beautiful.. this is what i get.* -my eyes burn- by matchbox romance. every word describes me My eyes burn from these tears You'd think I'd learn over the years Good things won't last forever So what the hell am I suppose to do You only wanted the things I couldn't give to you And you had it all anyway So take take everything and leave me scrambling Reaching for something that wasn't there in the first place I take back everything i've said You wore those words on your lips As if they meant anything anyway

deleted. pointless paragraphs again. 

heh i am just pathetic. n just for the record this has never happened me before. just for the record.. i have no idea what to do. cant count how many times ive said that in the past 3 weeks. and that right there in its self is sad.

deleted. big pointless paragraphs of me saying how much you mean to me. ----------------------------------------------------- i am listening to my ashley simpson cd!=) hehe its actually not that great. i really like only 3 of the songs but im listening to it b/c my mom hates it. shes getting on my nerves at the moment. i wish my stereo wouldnt have broke.. my ghetto boom box doesnt go very loud. heh but it'll do. ----------------------------------------------------- last night deanna came over at like 10:00 banging on my window.. haha it was so funny. i was like omg what is that n i hear deanna go "KELLY ITS ME DEANNA" haha so i let her in n we just hung out last night. took pictures.. "look sexy". haha us like choking our selves.. it was great fun=). ----------------------------------------------------- and today i got a new phone! heh a year of having my house phone.. tons of memories with that thing. ill miss it;). ---------------------------------------------------- so ne way. i talked to my long lost bestfriend today. she was supossed to stop by but im kind of doubting it now. i miss her a lot. --------------------------------------------------- things are way different now. its weird to think that a month ago everything was nothing out of the ordinary. i miss yall a lot. it was great while it lasted n i really will never forget all of our times together. each and every one of you are gorgegous inside and out and im so glad that i got the chance to get to know yall. i love you

hmm so im bored. y'know you really frustrate me... haha im begining to think that our future plans are not going to happen. ;)heh well i am very close to giving up. yeah.. about - <-- that close. i really dont want to but the more i think about it the more i know that it wouldnt be ok. the more i know i just SHOULD give up. n thats that. ha i guess. well, just so you know.. you were the first guy i really truly liked since begining of 9th grade. i liked you for you. and no offence but i dont think very many girls would say that. i prolly should have just told you, believe me.. i wanted to. but y'know maybe it was good that i didnt. i think its good that i didn't. i want you to like me(even if its just as friends) for me, my personality.. not just b/c i liked you. n i think thats just to much to ask for. so there-fore i am done trying to talk to you and hopefully i will just find some1 else. heh who needs guys ne way.. all they do is make you cry!;). kidding but ne how. im having a really good weekend=). def not looking forward to school though =) <33Kelly.

i just wrote a page long about you and i deleted all of it. blah..=/. 

im just being scared. im sorry n i dont expect u to wait for me.

im feelin a lot better. haha its amazing wut the littlest things can do. =). the mood swings are just killin me;). i still care about all that stuff i said but theres really no sense in getting upset over somthing thats never going to happen. i might as well just get over it. hah easier said then done but thats ok. i dont even know why i feel the way i feel ne ways.. i guess theres just somthing about you that pulls me in. i duno, it really is weird. and ive decided that no matter how i feel.. all of this really isnt worth it. it really isnt n hopefully i wont ever waste this much time thinking of you wen i probably never cross your mind. *ill wait for you but i cant wait forever* going to shannons n a lil bit =D! waitin for hurricane charlie to come blow me away=) haha. I LOVE YOU<3

so this is wut i do wen i get bored n i am def. bored. well i could be at shannons right now but i just dont feel like it. i dont know why but im just n such a blah mood.  i had a good day at school n everything its just some other things i guess.
i couldnt concentrate at all today. its funny how you want something you cant have. you frustrate me so bad. i wish wut you do didnt work.. i wish i was having fun at shannons rather then being upset about something that doesnt matter and wont matter. i wish you cared=(. i think im just tired. school is cutting my sleep by like 5 hours.

~hey there i know its hard to feel like i dont care at all. *and i cant make it on my own* you kill me, you know you do.. you kill me well ,you like it too and i can tell. you never stop until my final breath is gone. spare me just.. 3 last words i love you is all she heard ill wait for you but i cant wait forever. -Hawthorne Heights

its so weird that the person that i know so little about has become so important to me. i really dont understand why im being like this..i just like cant help it.. haha its so weird. but yeah, this has def. NEVER happened b4! n im sure in a few days this will all fade but honestly.. i dont really want it to. --you shouldnt judge people b4 you get to know them--
quote of the day! heh i gg. goin to the mall with lisa!
<33Kelly

well im bored n i have things on my mind so im just going to talk. read if you want.

hmm so 1st things 1st. im scared, and nervous and excited and hopeful n so many things right now. i really hope im making the right decision n that i wont regret wut im getting myself n to. im going to miss so much. it was truly such a great experience that i will never forget. you have totally changed me for the better and even if i hardly knew you im sure even in a small way, u made an impact on me. the way im seeing it is that either way a part of me is going to be missing. i will always cherish each and every one of you.

These are a few people that have been on my mind a lot lately (im not going to say names). well to start off.. i miss you so much. you have totally helped make me who i am and i owe so much to you. im so sorry that i never truly thanked you for everything you have done for me. im so sorry that i took u for granted n im sorry that things are like this now. ill hold on to every memory that we had together and ill always be waiting for your call. i love you

 

i will miss you. i know i will. and honestly, i dont understand why. you were the cause of so many of my bad days, and you would make me so mad. but at the same time you were the reason i would want to go to school, the reason i would go outta my way just to pass you in the hall..to not even get a glance. the reason i would stay online just to see if you'd IM me wen i knew that that would never happen. all along "you were everything i didnt know i always wanted". i have so much that i want to talk to you about.. i just want to talk to you. but that will never happen n my chances are pretty much squashed. i will never see you again and i will have to be ok with that.

 

last person for today: im sorry we didnt work out. it really is my fault and i completley understand if you dont want to talk to me as much ne more. i figured out that it really is to late to try to be like we were and thats my fault for waiting so long. i shouldnt have expected you to wait for me. our friendship meant a lot to me and you are a great person. i never intentionally meant to hurt you and i really hope you know that. we have had so many great times together and i truly have, will and still miss you. im always here for you n i hope to hear from you.

o yea! MARISSA! gosh i love you. we're doing sumthin this weekend ok? i miss you so much! aw n thanx for caring:-). i love you n im ALWAYS here for you no matter wut. u kno the #! 7 digits away:-). heh love you!
-ur cupcake! lol

this isnt supossed to be hard. i shouldnt have to go thru this. -sigh- i guess theres just sacrafices that have to be made to get wut u want. how come i thot it would be this easy?

here i go again with being the naive me and blowing everything outta proportion. 

im going to bed.
 
-kelly

havnt wrote n here n a while n no1 reads this so imma write n it. 

i really do miss you sumtimes. after all this time i still miss all our memories n how we were so close. no one will ever understand how i felt about you. how strong i felt n how i thot that nothing would come between us n that u wouldnt change n that everything just wouldnt change. naive perhaps? very. n thats my fault. all of this was my fault. im so sorrie. wow i hate thinking about this but gosh. gotta get it out sumtime rite? n my friends arent there for me on that level so ive always been stuck on my own with this thing. its ok tho. ive made it out alrite havnt i? im happier then ive ever been b4. n even tho i could always be happier.. im perfectly fine with the way things are. i love my life so much n its goin really good rite but i just cant stop thinking about it. i just cant. ill push it n the bak of my head for a day, a week maybe but it just comes bak n it haunts me. it haunts me till i just gotta deal with it n try to turn it nto a positive thing. no1 will ever replace you. i have come to that conclusion..i will never be as close with sum1 as i was with you. u dont kno how much u hurt me. i cant trust ne bodie. no1. maybe thats a good thing? if ya dont trust ppl then u dont get hurt n the long run rite? dont get close to ne1. *sigh* wut am i saying. i have so manie mixed feelings about this that its crazy. i just toss my thots around my head n they all contridict themselves. one minute im depressed about it n blaming you for doing this to me n the next im thinking positive saying that u made me to be the best person i can be n changed me n made me more mature n shaped me as a person. gosh, y did it take leaving me to make me see wut i was doing. god.. y couldnt u warn me? y couldnt u make me see? *sigh* regardless of it all. it was my fault. my dumbass self that ruined the best thing that ever happened to me. i will never forget you. i will never forget you. *sigh* i really miss you. im so sorrie. hate me. i deserve it. 
-kelly

im definitley not going to stoop to his level ne more. no more am i gonna call him silly names n act like im n middle school. he can say w/e he wants n its not gonna hurt me cuz i kno its bs :-)!

today was SOO awesome. life is so great. i love gettin up n the morning n just bein with my friends. 

read my xanga.  i never write n this thing

<3kelly :-D

im so glad that me n her are talking again n that its bcomin like old times. i never realized how much i missed our friendship=/. n i was wonderin earlyer 'where did everything go wrong' n i think i figured it out. hope so.. wow, things are definitley lookin up :-). these past two sumwut hard two weeks is about to be over :-). yayy:-) -kellyy

today was great :-D i love my friends. i would be nothing w/o them. i love yall :-) -kelly ps. o yea.. sumthin did happen today n it made everything worse but n a way its a good thing. actually, its a great thing bcuz i learned alot about sum ppl that make me a think a lot different of them. n since i kno now ill be savin myself from gettin hurt by them again. so it all worked out :-). everything happens for the best :-D

Trulykelly14: what? --: i still luv ya gurl Trulykelly14: =/ yea... aww that was juss the end of it but at the beggining i was really mad n she/he was the one sayin sorrie. if i said ne thing close to that now she/he would call me names n block me. -sigh- those were the days ..=/:-). my storage level went from 82 to 57%! woOp woOp! -kellyy

i really need u now
tell me things will be ok

make my tears go away
